{"tid":2221563,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"3G 》4G》5G 我地要幾耐先適應 ？","createTime":"2020-09-28T12:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T07:51:15.000Z","uid":73895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed535821466c673e5fa0bf62bd7ff200090d8ac2","tid":2221563,"uid":73895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"想當年成日都話要視像通話，所以當時D分鐘數印象係包 video call<br />\n而當年已覺得依類機好型，個鏡頭可以自由轉做前置或後置鏡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vj8FqDD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVj8FqDD.jpg&h=a5216b67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n進入4G年代，就好似無乜特出手機<br />\n但我地就習慣左 video call 時代，電訊商好似再無 video call 包埋<br />\n乜都係  Facetime  / 其他視像通訊<br />\n<br />\n到底進入 5G 時代嘅時候，我地嘅習慣又點樣慢慢起左變化 ？"},{"pid":"e62f99879d68a3af176905dc4fab1c58f3778949","tid":2221563,"uid":73895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a4ca65a1c4441d9638adc79025c7b72f449fb3","tid":2221563,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"視像通訊係咪多數都係情侶/遠房親戚溝通用？"},{"pid":"4332d2c81c77296a59d4edffcda6c2322df83829","tid":2221563,"uid":73895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11a4ca65a1c4441d9638adc79025c7b72f449fb3","tid":2221563,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"視像通訊係咪多數都係情侶/遠房親戚溝通用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當時係同情人玩過<br />\n<br />\n但而家FaceTime 變左同本地家人"},{"pid":"9d69bb5041e35df1bc338779372c0f564ddaf6b2","tid":2221563,"uid":73895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:51:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xpuojm5MgQg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dxpuojm5MgQg&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw